It has sometimes been suggested that the allusions in this passage are specifically to Roger Bacon and Descartes. But Descartes had not yet (1620) published any works, and, as he was only born in 1596, he cannot possibly have been alluded to by Bacon in the Cogitata et Visa, which was composed about 1607.
